{"tid":1555082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一手資料 捐錢 星火/612都會幫到義士 坊間太多謠言","createTime":"2019-09-09T08:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:05:24.000Z","uid":233453,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b44a23ff8440d18b613d539b4c85d398fa8a548","tid":1555082,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"各位手足 請放心 捐錢比星火/612<br />\n唔好再信 612唔幫義士 因為網上太多謠言 <br />\n以上係律師親口講（假既話 我不得好死）<br />\n因為全部人搵星火幫忙 每日被捕人士太多 <br />\n星火都係彈去612搵律師 <br />\n<br />\n多謝各位 和理非 勇士 <br />\n宜家d狗 四面包抄 好危險 <br />\n不被捕 不受傷 不分化 不割蓆<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"5b181892ccba342b633b127d29a3a854c67dd6d0","tid":1555082,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"你自己睇佢報告 睇完再傾"},{"pid":"0fcf474dd4fb91b6f4a0d546e1d3847a1fff2632","tid":1555082,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"推推 <br />\n一手律師親口講"},{"pid":"1fd98034d06dba994cff8281014b7837bbf3b254","tid":1555082,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:14:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52fde7a5f72c5cce5dda38f5ed09bbffa8202ac7","tid":1555082,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n<br />\n即係星火唔夠資源做唔切<br />\n612太多錢好得閒<br />\n<br />\n咁捐星火咪得囉"},{"pid":"fc587629afc21d6d564c99f1238bf7957ace04b6","tid":1555082,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52fde7a5f72c5cce5dda38f5ed09bbffa8202ac7","tid":1555082,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n<br />\n即係星火唔夠資源做唔切<br />\n612太多錢好得閒<br />\n<br />\n咁捐星火咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"意思係你搵星火 其實聯絡被捕人係612<br />\n實際上係用612嘅資金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}